    ğŸ” REST API

        REST = Representational State Transfer (an architectural style).
        Uses HTTP methods like:
        GET â€“ read data
        POST â€“ create
        PUT â€“ update
        DELETE â€“ remove

        RESTful APIs are stateless and use URLs + HTTP.

     âš™ï¸ Middleware

        Functions that run before your final route handler.
